code: @Override protected ListSerializer<T> createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<T> elementSerializer = (TypeSerializer<T>) nestedSerializers[0].     return new ListSerializer<>(elementSerializer). }
@Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(ListSerializer<T> outerSerializer) {     return new TypeSerializer<?>[] { outerSerializer.getElementSerializer() }. }
